      "content": "idk i dont want to talk to someone. it just feels like a loop. like if you look at it logically, if the universe is just infinite chaos and nothing has an actual objective purpose, then life and death are just two different states of being. they're basically equal. why is one forced on me while the other is seen as a \"problem\"?",
